## Filers

The `filers` endpoint takes the following parameters:

Parameter Name | Options
--- | ---
years | CSV list of years (example: 2018,2019)
states | two letter state code
msamds | 5 digit integer code
counties | 5 digit integer code

### Filers Example

> Example

 ```shell
